<MSG<FAC0006<ANP0200:0000:0004So, The Doctor's back,
huh?<NOD<CLR
Well, that sucks.<NOD<CLRStill, though, he was
kind of a pushover if
I remember right.<NOD<FAC0007<ANP0200:0030:0004
If I wasn't controlled by
the Demon Crown, I coulda
taken him out myself!<NOD<CLR<FAC0006Well, if Misery didn't
do it before me,
anyway...<NOD<END
#0201
<MSG<FAC0006I think I'll try to
look for Jenka in a bit.<NOD
If she's still alright...<NOD<END
#0220
<FLJ0256:0221<FL+0256
<KEY<MSG<FAC0038I suppose we were so
wrapped up in celebration,
back then...<NOD We could
have never guessed The
Doctor was still alive...<NOD<END
#0221
<KEY<MSG<FAC0038I'm sorry I can't be
of any help right now...<NOD
You're the last we have
that could take on this
threat.<NOD<CLR
Be safe, alright?<NOD<END
