<MS2Did you know I had a brother?<NOD
He and I were sent to this island
together, to destroy the source
of the Demon Crown's magic...<NOD<CLO<WAI0100
<KEY<MSG<FAC0038...Kazuma Sakamoto.<NOD
Are you professor
Booster's messenger?<NOD<CLO<FAC0000<CMU0030<FAI0003<WAI0010
<MSG<FAC0001Aha!<NOD I was wondering when
you were getting here.<NOD
I'm Curly Brace, nice to
meet you!<NOD<CLR<FAC0038
A-and Balrog, I see.<NOD<CLR<FAC0007<ANP0200:0030:0002
Hi, Kazuma!<NOD<CLO<FAC0000<WAI0100<MSG<FAC0038
So, erm...<NOD<CLRAny sign of Booster or
my mother around here?<NOD
They actually left for the
island ahead of me while
I tended to things...<NOD<CLR<FAC0003
Oh?<NOD<CLRHe said you two were
leaving seperately,<NOD
but I think you were
the first to get here...<NOD
I haven't heard a thing
from anyone else yet.<NOD<CLR<FAC0002I guess they got so
wrapped-up in preparing to
evacuate the island...<NOD<CLR<FAC0038Hold on, evacuate the
island!?<NOD What in the world
is going on here?<NOD<CLR<FAC0003
Well...<NOD<SOU0043<CMU0000<WAI0010<CLR<FAC0000
...?<NOD<CLO<MYD0000<FON0500:0016
